{"tid":1299244,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽人講林鄭會睇連登","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:51:25.000Z","uid":68930,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a14cd162a39647312f6b97b7124e7dd53923ab70","tid":1299244,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"有咩想同佢講?我講先<br />\n<br />\n1)因為我地唔信你，所以只接受有正式定義效力嘅「徹回」<br />\n2)因為我地唔信警監會，(往蹟你自己搵人搵)，所以一定要另外嘅獨立調查委員會<br />\n3)因為你嘅失敗再加高壓手段，所以所有人(不包括撐警嘅藍絲廢老)係反送中活動中因反送中而犯嘅罪行都係政府單一為因嘅錯，所以一定要停止追求，全部釋放<br />\n4)唔好叫人信你，你冇任何野值得我地信<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，唔好成日諗點解過去兩年咁平靜係你功勞，只係因為比梁振英搞到好煩嘅回溯，你做咁耐一啲功勞都冇，你嘅行為係一個賣港賊</span></span>"},{"pid":"a08a75b933c838d8be6ac8b920906b6dd5cf56ce","tid":1299244,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"林太負評"},{"pid":"a49ee51f720ef4b5c26dbb676e75f8539147b934","tid":1299244,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b169c157474c36958dde4c0cfc680cac001e96","tid":1299244,"uid":3194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"我只有一句同佢講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母死臭閪天堂地獄都唔撚收你呀仆街死全家啦你</span></span>"},{"pid":"5344816c732c01414a1fa092bb26ede96ca7f78c","tid":1299244,"uid":68930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2b169c157474c36958dde4c0cfc680cac001e96","tid":1299244,"uid":3194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"我只有一句同佢講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母死臭閪天堂地獄都唔撚收你呀仆街死全家啦你</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"請撐林鄭落地獄"},{"pid":"bf2ad898299887b0b375ec3ee6072cad10f24365","tid":1299244,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit